{"tid":2360958,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"街坊：庭上未提關鍵鏡頭被拆","createTime":"2021-01-10T08:53:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-10T10:36:08.000Z","uid":25558,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"fc3830a8dde414f57474ea6facbb01eefe5ece13","tid":2360958,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T08:53:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210110/7RSPBEMUZFBSZKZB2LTNHAUXIY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210110%2F7RSPBEMUZFBSZKZB2LTNHAUXIY%2F&d=3UqZ%2FPYEUq8PtOmaimGdDajPH3pfKCXBWMLigY0rPLs%3D&h=fc76ed8a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210110%2F7RSPBEMUZFBSZKZB2LTNHAUXIY%2F&h=17ddd6df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210110/7RSPBEMUZFBSZKZB2LTNHAUXIY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n街坊：庭上未提關鍵鏡頭被拆<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】死因研訊期間，作供警務。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：科大學生會：校長變臉令人失望<br />\n<br />\n「消失的鏡頭」由尚德街坊Mac發現，他從小居於尚德邨，熟悉案發停車場環境。他翻遍死因研訊的報道，庭上始終未有提及3樓停車場一個關鍵鏡頭，上月更發現該鏡頭已被拆除，於是告訴周爸爸。<br />\n<br />\n「我一路覺得，諗住應該咁大件事係有人講嘅，照計唔會冇人發覺㗎？就算佢『裝假狗』都會有人講啦。」消失的鏡頭位於停車場3樓升降機對面，有可能拍到升降機及事發周邊環境。Mac認為，鏡頭位置關鍵，「可以睇到係周梓樂自己一個，定係有其他人係附近」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：17歲FA目睹血泊中的梓樂  哭過痛過愧疚過「嚮往周爸爸堅強」<br />\n<br />\n庭上披露，停車場升降機的閉路電視其實沒有裝設鏡頭，Mac認為，3樓鏡頭即使未能拍到案發情況，至少可證明當時是否有人使用升降機。<br />\n<br />\nMac說，。。。。。。。。。。。。，認為警方在現場搜證時，理應發現上述鏡頭，惟庭上供詞卻顯示，「（警方）好似唔知道咁，係做嘢俹簁得滯，唔睇或故意唔睇都唔奇」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/-3R6I7pe669lBw02DEdSfNBRR8Q=/817x402/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SP7FULL2VZCXRJAWWWVEXKJNGY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F-3R6I7pe669lBw02DEdSfNBRR8Q%3D%2F817x402%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSP7FULL2VZCXRJAWWWVEXKJNGY.gif&h=0d75bf17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■案發後兩日，Mac曾拍下停車場3樓「消失的鏡頭」（紅圈示，左圖）；鏡頭其後在停車場翻新時被拆除（紅圈示，右圖）。受訪者提供圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n指警供詞不實 側門未被鎖<br />\n<br />\n聆訊期間，有警員及管理公司職員均供稱，尚禮樓通往3樓停車場的側門被鎖上，Mac則指出與事實不符。他曾於周梓樂出事翌日途經該處，發現側門的門鎖掉落，原先大門亦會以木條或鐵鏈插入門柄鎖門，「（當時）嗰門柄係甩咗落嚟」，僅剩電磁鎖鎖起側門，「我一拉呢，基本上道門就開咗」。<br />\n<br />\n他已將資料告知周爸爸，不過最終資料未有用於庭上，Mac認為，即使所知再微小，亦有必要知會周爸爸及公眾，「。。<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n領展表示，上述閉路電視由領展持有，但於2011年停車場進行優化工程後，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/RGQx_-g0LY-uRTOr2oOJcalqZMA=/1721x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/EFZHP2RXMJBYFPR654JNQNJ4EY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FRGQx_-g0LY-uRTOr2oOJcalqZMA%3D%2F1721x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FEFZHP2RXMJBYFPR654JNQNJ4EY.jpg&h=ee11433a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■街坊Mac認為，案件有不少疑團，即使鏡頭已棄用，警方亦有責任查證。"},{"pid":"1820865caae47271dd7ca0fd82264696e8088359","tid":2360958,"uid":325484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T08:56:33.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbaf1570d6361fa8cebc55f50f7c9904f270e049","tid":2360958,"uid":15205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T10:00:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e7a54b9d7d701489dcc8346ea57f42ebdfa60d5","tid":2360958,"uid":222970,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T10:03:16.000Z","msg":"當然唔上得庭，因為一睇就先邊個做！"},{"pid":"ffd500a57f38c80fa53fdf50c6e1ba81a64c6c85","tid":2360958,"uid":272075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T10:12:24.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/